Please download XXE from http://www.xmlmind.com/xmleditor/

Install the xxe.jar into your local maven repository (adjust the path for your system, this is an example from OS X)

Ensure that XXE is EXACTLY the version you are installing!

mvn install:install-file -Dfile=/Applications/XMLEditor.app/Contents/Resources/Java/xxe.jar -DgroupId=com.xmlmind -DartifactId=xxe -Dversion=3.6.1 -Dpackaging=jar
